                p This project came about for a couple of reasons. One of the main reasons, was new research and information had come out since some of the earliest Agroforestry Notes were written and our team wanted to update them to be more current, relevant, but most importantly - more accurate.  We would also no longer be re-printing these items as they went out of stock. We found that as our online PDFs became more popular we were finding there was less of a need to print out this particular serious. However, our audience was still interested in the material, based on analytics results we studied. 

            
            section
